    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/a6d1b7fbbe85492f4121f0b6e078ad52.avif?t=1734614083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras_big/a6d1b7fbbe85492f4121f0b6e078ad52.avif?t=1734614083 width=800 height=240 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在社交推理类 TPS 游戏《Zoomies》中释放您的智慧！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入我们的主题公园，与好友一同沉浸在《Zoomies》带来的狂野刺激中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >猎捕四处乱窜的【栩栩如生的机械动物】，并揭开其他玩家隐藏的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关键很简单：保持专注！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/77998c980674cfd7afef9522e023c83e.poster.avif?t=1734614083\" width=680 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/77998c980674cfd7afef9522e023c83e.webm?t=1734614083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/77998c980674cfd7afef9522e023c83e.mp4?t=1734614083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要让其他玩家离开您的视线。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/5f073aa497520299d3af14cdd7339506.avif?t=1734614083\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras_big/5f073aa497520299d3af14cdd7339506.avif?t=1734614083 width=800 height=240 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义角色！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/a46a5facd75978b412cca8414f87f9d8.poster.avif?t=1734614083\" width=758 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/a46a5facd75978b412cca8414f87f9d8.webm?t=1734614083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/a46a5facd75978b412cca8414f87f9d8.mp4?t=1734614083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >展现您的个性！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为您的角色打造独一无二的风格，让自己在游戏中脱颖而出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>和好友一起玩！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/36e730cc5bc9937a7d55d29aaaf2b475.poster.avif?t=1734614083\" width=776 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/36e730cc5bc9937a7d55d29aaaf2b475.webm?t=1734614083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/36e730cc5bc9937a7d55d29aaaf2b475.mp4?t=1734614083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与好友组队，体验更有趣、更激烈的对抗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Zoomies》是一款多人游戏，合作游玩时乐趣倍增。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>发现您的秘密角色！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/c1f30126a807c7bb95c3f23a8921d02e.poster.avif?t=1734614083\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/c1f30126a807c7bb95c3f23a8921d02e.webm?t=1734614083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/c1f30126a807c7bb95c3f23a8921d02e.mp4?t=1734614083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位玩家都会分配一个秘密的<strong>角色</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些角色是收集动物和赚取积分的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心隐藏自己的角色，不要让其他人察觉——您会很快明白其中的奥妙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>紧张刺激的狩猎！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/786659353be425f6398aed2e78aed1e4.poster.avif?t=1734614083\" width=796 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/786659353be425f6398aed2e78aed1e4.webm?t=1734614083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/786659353be425f6398aed2e78aed1e4.mp4?t=1734614083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追逐并捕捉在场地中乱跑的动物，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将它们带回，赢取积分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成特定组合还能获得额外奖励积分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请记住：最高分并不总是意味着胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏好您的<strong>角色</strong>，同时<strong>仔细观察他人</strong>，逆转战局就在一念之间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>猜测其他玩家的角色！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/145b8767e8ef82f4bad1d253248ad77f.poster.avif?t=1734614083\" width=776 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/145b8767e8ef82f4bad1d253248ad77f.webm?t=1734614083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009430/extras/145b8767e8ef82f4bad1d253248ad77f.mp4?t=1734614083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分享您的观察，尝试推断其他玩家的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您猜对了，他们的奖励积分将被扣除。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制定聪明的策略吧！正确的推断将为您的胜利铺平道路！</p>",
